      "instruction": "<p>Heat a large, wide-based pan (preferably non-stick) with a drizzle of <strong>olive oil</strong> over a medium-high heat</p><p>Once hot, add the <strong>chopped pepper</strong>, <strong>crushed garlic </strong>and<strong> chopped shallot </strong>with a small splash of <strong>cold</strong> <strong>water </strong>and cook for 5 min or until slightly softened</p>",
