    {
      "instruction": "<p>Slice your <strong>gluten free</strong> <strong>brioche buns</strong> in half</p><p>Add the <strong>halved</strong> <strong>brioche</strong> to a baking tray and put the tray in the oven for 3-4 min or until warmed through</p><p>Wash then remove the<span class=\"text-danger\"> </span><strong>leaves </strong>from the<strong> lettuce </strong>for 1 per person, pat it dry with kitchen paper and set aside</p><p>Chop the<strong> inner core</strong> into quarters, lengthways</p>",
