    {
      "instruction": "<p>To build, layer the <strong>toasted brioche base </strong>with a <strong>lettuce leaf</strong>, a wedge of <strong>pepper</strong> and the<strong> peri-peri halloumi</strong></p><p>Dollop over the <strong>peri-nnaise </strong>and top with a <strong>toasted brioche lid</strong> – this is your <strong>peri-peri halloumi burger</strong></p><p>Serve the <strong>peri-peri halloumi burger </strong>with the<strong> fries</strong>, <strong>lettuce wedges </strong>and any <strong>remaining peri-nnaise</strong> to the side</p><p>Enjoy!</p>",
